ygData.msgSnippet: Level 49 is still open, yes? *sigh*  3 out of 50 songs being a charm song,  now THAT is just wrong.. Bien
ygData.messageBody:
Level 49 is still open, yes?

*sigh* 3 out of 50 songs being a charm song, now THAT is just wrong..

Bien

> -----Original Message-----
> From: Kevin L. Crawford [SMTP:Lyrnia@...]
> Sent: Wednesday, April 12, 2000 11:44 AM
> To: eqbards@egroups.com
> Subject: [eqbards] Not sure, but here's my guess for the new 45th
> level song
>
> This song looks like an AWESOME candidate to twist in with our Charm
> tactic. However it comes awful late to be truely useful.
>
> 1) Charm Mob
> 2) Haste/buff mob w/1 song
> 3) Selo's
>
> Rinse, Repeat
>
> Even if the NPC your 'pet' is taking down is lower level this song will
> probably give it enough of a boost to win, almost every time.
>
> I see a use, albeit a limited one.
>
> Anyone else notice that we're going to need ANOTHER charm upgrade
> somewhere in the 50's? 39th will only take us to 49th level npc's.
>
> Lyrnia
